        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite: Proficiency in @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-rules.JournalEntry.rv19GFzEa0nMTuAF.JournalEntryPage.A5vSPTTu7J1k8HA9#medicine]{Medicine}</strong></em></p><p><em>You spend time during your rest tending to the wounds of your allies.</em></p><p><strong>During a Short Rest</strong> - 6 Creatures</p><p>When you and your allies take a short rest, you choose up to 6 allied creatures who expend at least one hit die to heal, including yourself. </p><ul><li><p>The chosen creatures regain additional hit points equal to your level.</p></li></ul>",
